Package net.sf.jclal.core

The package contains the core of the framework.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAlgorithm
    Algorithm interface.
    IAlgorithmListener
    Algorithm listener.
    IBatchMode
    Interface for batch mode active learning.
    IClassifier
    Interface for the classifiers to be used in the framework.
    IConfigure
    Class for the configuration of the experiments.
    IDataset
    Interface that represents a dataset.
    IEvaluation
    It represents a interface for all Evaluation Metrics.
    IEvaluationMethod
    Evaluation method used to analyze the performance of the experiment.
    IOracle
    Interface that represents an Oracle.
    IQueryStrategy
    Interface for Active Learning Query Strategies.
    ISampling

    IScenario

    Interface for the Stop Criterion classes.
    ISystem

    IXMLConfigurationBuilder

    JCLAL
    Root for the JCLAL hierarchy.
